# Facial Expression Recognition using Keras and OpenCV

## Project Overview

This project detects human facial expressions from images and live webcam video using Deep Learning.

The model classifies emotions into the following categories:

- Angry
- Disgust
- Fear
- Happy
- Sad
- Surprise
- Neutral

The project uses the FER2013 dataset and a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN).

---

## Features

✔ Face Detection

✔ Emotion Recognition

✔ Live Webcam Prediction

✔ Image Prediction

✔ CNN Model

✔ OpenCV Integration

---

## Dataset

FER2013

Download:

https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/msambare/fer2013

Place the dataset inside

dataset/FER2013

