## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/username/Facial-Expression-Recognition-OpenCV-Keras.git

cd Facial-Expression-Recognition-OpenCV-Keras
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Train Model

```bash
python src/train.py
```

---

## Webcam Detection

```bash
python src/webcam.py
```

---

## Predict Image

```bash
python src/predict.py
```

---

## Results

Training Accuracy:
95%

Validation Accuracy:
72-75%

